e code, and response contains both code and desc</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong><u>Request : </u></stro=
ng></p><p>&nbsp;"gender": {</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=
;&nbsp;"code":&nbsp;"M"</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;},</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;=
